<p>The ATACMS SLEP missile (Figure 5) is a "bridging" initiative that will provide time to complete analysis and development of a successor capability to the aging ATACMS stockpile, and non-compliant CM missiles. The SLEP will refurbish/replace propulsion and navigation systems; replace the non-compliant anti-personnel/anti-materiel warhead with the current unitary blast/fragmentation warhead, and add a proximity fuze option to obtain area effects.</p>
